# 📋 Crewera Reality — All Form Structures (Updated v2)

> **30 Forms** · **~350 Fields** · Advanced Property Request with Compulsory ROI

---

## 🔄 Property Listing Workflow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A["👤 User submits\nProperty Request\n(ROI compulsory)"] --> B["👑 Admin reviews\nROI & Financials"]
    B -->|Reject| C["❌ Rejected\n(with reason)"]
    B -->|Approve| D["✅ Approved"]
    D --> E["👤 User completes\nFULL property details"]
    E --> F["👑 Admin verifies\n& Lists property"]
    G["👑 Admin can also\ndirectly Add Property\n(8-step wizard)"] --> F
```

> **Admin can do EVERYTHING** — add properties directly, approve/reject requests, edit any property, manage all data.

---

## Conventions

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| ✅ | Required |
| ⬜ | Optional |
| 📎 | File Upload |
| 🔽 | Dropdown / Select |
| 💰 | Financial / ROI Field |

