### Form 13: 🏗️ Property Listing Request — Multi-Step (5 Steps)

> **Advanced form with compulsory ROI.** Admin reviews financials before approval.

#### Step 1: Your Information (All Required)

| # | Field | Type | Req |
|---|-------|------|-----|
| 1 | Your Name | `text` | ✅ |
| 2 | Your Email | `email` | ✅ |
| 3 | Your Phone | `tel` | ✅ |
| 4 | Your Address | `textarea` | ✅ |

#### Step 2: Property Details

| # | Field | Type | Req |
|---|-------|------|-----|
| 5 | Project Name | `text` | ✅ |
| 6 | Property Type | 🔽 Residential / Commercial / Mixed / Industrial | ✅ |
| 7 | Special Type | 🔽 None / Pent House / Duplex / Triplex / Villa / Bungalow / Farmhouse | ⬜ |
| 8 | Builder/Developer Name | `text` | ⬜ |
| 9 | Description | `textarea` | ⬜ |
| 10 | BHK Type | `text` e.g. 2 BHK, 3 BHK, Commercial | ⬜ |
| 11 | Total Units | `number` | ⬜ |
| 12 | Available Units | `number` | ⬜ |
| 13 | Size — Super Buildup (sqft) | `number` | ⬜ |
| 14 | Size — Carpet (sqft) | `number` | ⬜ |
| 15 | Facing | 🔽 E / W / N / S / NE / NW / SE / SW | ⬜ |

#### Step 3: Location & Construction

| # | Field | Type | Req |
|---|-------|------|-----|
| 16 | Property Location (Address) | `textarea` | ✅ |
| 17 | City | 🔽 city list | ⬜ |
| 18 | State | 🔽 state list | ⬜ |
| 19 | Pincode | `text` 6 digits | ⬜ |
| 20 | Landmarks | `textarea` | ⬜ |
| 21 | Construction Stage | 🔽 Pre-Launch / Under Construction / Ready to Move | ⬜ |
| 22 | Project Start Date | `date` | ⬜ |
| 23 | Expected Completion | `date` | ⬜ |
| 24 | Possession Date | `date` | ⬜ |

#### Step 4: 💰 Pricing & ROI (ROI is COMPULSORY)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **ROI, Price Per Unit, and Expected Revenue are COMPULSORY.** Admin will evaluate the request based on these financial metrics.

