|---|-------|------|-----|
| 25 | 💰 Price Per Unit (₹) | `number` | ✅ |
| 26 | 💰 Price Per Sqft (₹) | `number` | ⬜ |
| 27 | 💰 Total Project Cost (₹) | `number` | ⬜ |
| 28 | 💰 Expected Revenue (₹) | `number` | ✅ |
| 29 | 💰 **ROI (%)** | `number` 0–100, 2 decimal | **✅ COMPULSORY** |
| 30 | 💰 Rental Yield (%) | `number` | ⬜ |
| 31 | 💰 Expected Appreciation (%) | `number` | ⬜ |
| 32 | 💰 Booking Amount (₹) | `number` | ⬜ |
| 33 | Price Negotiable | `toggle` | ⬜ |

#### Step 5: Supporting Info & Contacts

| # | Field | Type | Req |
|---|-------|------|-----|
| 34 | Request Reason / Why List? | `textarea` | ⬜ |
| 35 | Proposed Amenities | `multi-checkbox` from amenity catalog | ⬜ |
| 36 | Photos | 📎 `file` multiple, jpg/png, Max 10MB | ⬜ |
| 37 | Video URL | `url` YouTube/Vimeo | ⬜ |
| 38 | Brochure | 📎 `file` pdf, Max 25MB | ⬜ |
| 39 | Financial Documents | 📎 `file` pdf/xlsx, Max 25MB | ⬜ |
| 40 | Contact Person Name | `text` | ⬜ |
| 41 | Contact Person Phone | `tel` | ⬜ |
| 42 | Contact Person Email | `email` | ⬜ |
| 43 | Contact Person Designation | `text` | ⬜ |

