## 📊 Summary

| Category | Forms | Key Forms |
|----------|-------|-----------|
| 🏠 Public | 7 | Registration, Inquiry, Contact |
| 🔒 User | 8 | **Property Request (5-step + ROI)**, Post-Approval Completion, Review |
| 👑 Admin | 15 | **Add Property (8-step wizard)**, Request Review, Lead Mgmt, Blog |
| **Total** | **30** | |

> [!TIP]
> **Form 13** (Property Request) has **43 fields across 5 steps** with compulsory ROI.
> **Form 14** (Post-Approval Completion) has **63 fields across 8 sections** — everything needed to list.
> **Form 16** (Admin Add Property) has **80+ fields across 8 steps** — the most comprehensive form.
